!Sample_data_processing = Seurat processing in R: counts from the "sample_filtered_feature_bc_matrix/matrix.mtx.gz" file generated by CellRanger were imported into R using the readMM() function from the Matrix package and used to construct a Seurat object for analysis. Demultiplexing of cells on the basis of hashtag oligos to assign cells to time points was performed using the HTODemux() function from Seurat. Samples corresponding to the top 5% of  counts for the A03_FLU_IK9 and A03_EBV_RK9 were removed from the data set because staining for those specificities was poor. TCR counts were imported from the "multi/vdj_t/filtered_contig_annotations.csv" file. For clustering, dimensionality reduction, differential expression, and other analysis, genes matching the following regular expression "^TR[ABDG][VJC]" were removed so that clustering would not be driven by clonotype-specific TCR gene expression. Only cells that were unambiguously assigned to a by HTO (HTO_classification.global == "Singlet") were included in the filtered data set.
!Sample_data_processing = Assembly: GRCh38-2020-A
!Sample_data_processing = Supplementary files format and content: tsv: tab separated values and tsv.gz: gzip-compressed tab-separated values.
!Sample_data_processing = Library strategy: CITE-seq
